details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: Sidney made such a mess! It's unbelievable! And now I will have to endure his company all the way to Rubyport. *sigh*

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: It can't be helped. Soldier! Go tell the guards to bring him in and we will depart.

details.name: Scout
details.text: Sir! Sir! I have important news!

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: What is it? Catch your breath and tell me.

details.name: Scout
details.text: It's Sapphire Dawn! They are everywhere! Have a look!

details.name: Scout
details.text: They are already setting up blockades.

details.name: Scout
details.text: But that is not all! We've got emergency transmission from Lord Dawson. Sapphire Dawn is already assaulting our border. You are being ordered to return as quickly as possible and organize defense.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: What are we waiting for then! Organize Sidney's forces and go home!

details.name: Scout
details.text: I don't think we can, Sir.

details.name: Scout
details.text: Sapphire Dawn gathered huge forces on the other side of the river. They are ready to strike on our positions. If we try to move now, they will surely take advantage and wipe us out.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: This is really bad. Looks like our best chance is to sneak past them with a small detachment. Noble Sidney will have to stay here for a little longer...

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: My goal is to reach that road. Looks like Sapphire Dawn is using some of the Amber Noon towers to supply themselves.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: We have barracks and a single tower here. Our resources are going to be really stretched, but it will have to do.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: My passive ability allows me to get additional 5AP from every tower, each turn. It is not much, but it stacks up.

details.name: Scout
details.text: We have been spotted!

details.name: Tank
details.text: You have nowhere to run. Surrender now!

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: I'm afraid that is out of the question. We have to deal with that Tank somehow. I can deal significant damage to it, but constant fighting might wear me down, so I have to be careful.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: I have to move, there is no time to lose.

details.name: Mobile Infantry
details.text: Mobile Infantry ready to support you, Sir.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: This is exactly what I needed. These motorized units are much faster than regular Infantry. They are ideal for quick capture jobs. Their weaponry is not as good, so they can't attack flying targets, though it seems it will not be an issue at this time.

details.name: Mobile Infantry
details.text: We also have some experience Sir, so we can use our abilities to heal soldiers and even repair vehicles. It costs AP though. We will do what we can to keep you in this fight!

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: I can recruit more Mobile Infantry units in the barracks if need be.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: What is Sapphire Dawn doing here? And attacking our lands as well? Have Amber Noon asked them for help? Or are they just using an opportunity?

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: No matter. I am needed at our border.

details.name: Gentleman Archibald
details.text: I have failed you, my lord! Please forgive me!
